{"id": 2919, "source": "pestle", "subject": "physics", "course": null, "level": "SL", "paper": "1", "year": "2021", "session": "21M", "subtopic": "5-4-magnetic-effects-of-electric-currents", "title": "21M.1.SL.TZ1.21", "topic_id": "5", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>A long straight vertical conductor carries a current <em>I</em> upwards. An electron moves with horizontal speed <em>v</em> to the right.</p>\n<p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;\"/></p>\n<p>What is the direction of the magnetic force on the electron?</p>\n<p>A. Downwards</p>\n<p>B. Upwards</p>\n<p>C. Into the page</p>\n<p>D. Out of the page</p>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>A</p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n[N/A]\n</div>"}